1. **Broker-agnostic design** - All components must work across different brokers
2. **Type safety** - Comprehensive type hints and validation
3. **Modularity** - Clear separation of concerns and reusable components
4. **Robustness** - Graceful error handling and fallback mechanisms
5. **Performance** - Efficient data processing for real-time trading
6. **Maintainability** - Consistent patterns and comprehensive documentation
